DOPE++ (=Distributed Object Programing Environment for C++) is a C++ Template
library for pickling / programing in heterogenous network environments. 
NOTE: this is work in progress - alpha (perhaps pre-alpha) and there is 
no stable API yet.

The documentation is in the doc directory. 
For the license see doc/COPYING

